          <p>
            Kleva provides an AI-powered debt collection platform designed for financial 
            institutions in Latin America. Our Service includes:
          </p>
          <ul>
            <li>AI voice agents for automated debt collection calls</li>
            <li>Multi-channel communication (voice, SMS, WhatsApp)</li>
            <li>Real-time analytics and reporting</li>
            <li>Compliance management tools</li>
            <li>Integration with existing banking systems</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2>3. Use License</h2>
