            <li>Provide accurate and complete registration information</li>
            <li>Maintain the security of your account credentials</li>
            <li>Notify us immediately of any unauthorized access</li>
            <li>Accept responsibility for all activities under your account</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2>5. Data Processing</h2>
          <p>
            By using the Service, you acknowledge that:
          </p>
          <ul>
            <li>Kleva will process debtor data on your behalf</li>
            <li>You maintain ownership of all customer data</li>
            <li>You have obtained necessary consents for data processing</li>
            <li>Kleva will handle data in accordance with our Privacy Policy</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2>6. Compliance</h2>
          <p>
            You represent and warrant that your use of the Service will comply with all 
            applicable laws and regulations, including but not limited to:
          </p>
          <ul>
            <li>Local debt collection laws in your jurisdiction</li>
            <li>Consumer protection regulations</li>
            <li>Data privacy laws (LGPD, etc.)</li>
            <li>Telecommunications regulations</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2>7. Payment Terms</h2>
          <p>
            Payment terms are specified in your Service Agreement. You agree to:
          </p>
          <ul>
            <li>Pay all fees according to the agreed schedule</li>
            <li>Provide valid payment information</li>
            <li>Pay any applicable taxes</li>
          </ul>
          <p>
            Kleva reserves the right to suspend Service for non-payment after 30 days notice.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2>8. Service Level Agreement</h2>
          <p>
            Kleva commits to:
          </p>
          <ul>
            <li>99.9% platform uptime (excluding scheduled maintenance)</li>
            <li>24/7 technical support for critical issues</li>
            <li>Regular security updates and patches</li>
            <li>Data backup and recovery procedures</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
