            Both parties agree to maintain the confidentiality of any proprietary information 
            shared during the course of the Service relationship.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2>11. Limitation of Liability</h2>
          <p>
            TO THE MAXIMUM EXTENT PERMITTED BY LAW, KLEVA SHALL NOT BE LIABLE FOR ANY 
            INDIRECT, INCIDENTAL, SPECIAL, CONSEQUENTIAL, OR PUNITIVE DAMAGES, INCLUDING 
            LOST PROFITS, LOST DATA, OR BUSINESS INTERRUPTION.
          </p>
          <p>
            Kleva's total liability shall not exceed the amount paid by you for the Service 
            in the twelve months preceding the claim.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2>12. Indemnification</h2>
          <p>
            You agree to indemnify and hold Kleva harmless from any claims arising from:
          </p>
          <ul>
            <li>Your violation of these Terms</li>
            <li>Your violation of applicable laws or regulations</li>
            <li>Your use of the Service</li>
            <li>Any dispute between you and debtors</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2>13. Termination</h2>
          <p>
            Either party may terminate these Terms with 60 days written notice. Upon 
